data.title: Cat-Cow Stretch
instruction: Start on all fours with hands under shoulders and knees under hips
Arch your back, lifting your head and tailbone towards the ceiling (Cow)
Round your spine, tucking your chin and tailbone towards your chest (Cat)
Alternate between the two positions in a slow and controlled manner

data.title: Dead Bug
instruction: Lie on your back with arms extended towards the ceiling and knees bent at 90 degrees
Lower one arm and the opposite leg towards the floor while keeping your core engaged
Return to the starting position and alternate sides
